<p><strong>Author:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pr0m37h3um" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3628082); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3628082&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721493" alt="pr0m37h3um" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3628082)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pr0m37h3um" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3628082); return false;">pr0m37h3um</a></span><br />
A tale that I decided to write to contextualize <a href="/scp-4320">SCP-4320</a>. And also I wanted to write a creation myth. It's also the first installment in my new series about <a href="/scp-4320">SCP-4320</a>.</p>
<p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kingdeis" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3523889); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3523889&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721493" alt="KingDeis" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3523889)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kingdeis" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3523889); return false;">KingDeis</a></span> and SYwaves on the SCPD Discord for critique and advice.</p>
